{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-09",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_09_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Brigid",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 4,
  "page_start_sec": 488.93,
  "page_end_sec": 729.28,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.559,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 488.93,
      "end": 490.54,
      "text": "I suppose you do now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.76,
      "end": 491.3,
      "text": "she said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.42,
      "end": 492.76,
      "text": "looking at her sandwich again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.9,
      "end": 493.92,
      "text": "her face serious."
    },
    {
      "start": 494.84,
      "end": 495.136,
      "text": "But oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 495.83,
      "end": 497.34,
      "text": "I'm so tired of it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 497.36,
      "end": 498.18,
      "text": "and I do so"
    },
    {
      "start": 498.24,
      "end": 499.6,
      "text": "hate having to talk about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.288,
      "end": 500.68,
      "text": "Wouldn't it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 500.8,
      "end": 504.42,
      "text": "wouldn't it be just as well to wait and let you learn about"
    },
    {
      "start": 504.42,
      "end": 505.6,
      "text": "it as you say you will?"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.56,
      "end": 507.14,
      "text": "Spade laughed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 508.12,
      "end": 508.62,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 509.24,
      "end": 510.68,
      "text": "You'll have to figure that out for yourself.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 511.5,
      "end": 514.22,
      "text": "My way of learning is to heave a wild and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 514.22,
      "end": 516.28,
      "text": "unpredictable monkey wrench into the machinery."
    },
    {
      "start": 517.18,
      "end": 518.16,
      "text": "It's all right with me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 518.24,
      "end": 520.92,
      "text": "if you're sure none of the flying pieces will hurt you."
    },
    {
      "start": 521.88,
      "end": 523.63,
      "text": "She moved her bare shoulders uneasily,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 523.8,
      "end": 524.7,
      "text": "but said nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 525.4,
      "end": 527.3,
      "text": "For several minutes they ate in silence,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 527.52,
      "end": 528.94,
      "text": "he phlegmatically,"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.18,
      "end": 530.0,
      "text": "she thoughtfully."
    },
    {
      "start": 530.7,
      "end": 531.94,
      "text": "Then she said in a hushed voice,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 532.16,
      "end": 533.22,
      "text": "I'm afraid of you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.32,
      "end": 534.26,
      "text": "and that's the truth."
    },
    {
      "start": 535.18,
      "end": 535.54,
      "text": "He said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 535.7,
      "end": 536.98,
      "text": "that's not the truth."
    },
    {
      "start": 538.12,
      "end": 538.5,
      "text": "It is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 538.6,
      "end": 540.38,
      "text": "she insisted in the same low voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 541.08,
      "end": 543.18,
      "text": "I know two men I'm afraid of,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 543.22,
      "end": 544.72,
      "text": "and I've seen both of them tonight."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.62,
      "end": 547.8,
      "text": "I can understand your being afraid of Cairo,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 548.0,
      "end": 548.58,
      "text": "Spade said."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.12,
      "end": 549.99,
      "text": "He's out of your reach."
    },
    {
      "start": 551.12,
      "end": 551.64,
      "text": "And you aren't?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 552.76,
      "end": 553.32,
      "text": "Not that way,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 553.48,
      "end": 554.68,
      "text": "he said and grinned."
    },
    {
      "start": 555.18,
      "end": 556.22,
      "text": "She blushed."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.0,
      "end": 559.54,
      "text": "She picked up a slice of bread encrusted with gray liverwurst.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 560.26,
      "end": 561.4,
      "text": "She put it down on her plate.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 561.9,
      "end": 563.76,
      "text": "She wrinkled her white forehead and she said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 564.56,
      "end": 565.4,
      "text": "It's a black figure,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 565.58,
      "end": 566.28,
      "text": "as you know."
    },
    {
      "start": 566.976,
      "end": 567.74,
      "text": "Smooth and shiny.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 568.26,
      "end": 568.69,
      "text": "Of a bird."
    },
    {
      "start": 569.36,
      "end": 570.26,
      "text": "A hawk or falcon.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 570.74,
      "end": 571.44,
      "text": "about that high."
    },
    {
      "start": 572.3,
      "end": 573.66,
      "text": "She held her hands a foot apart.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 574.64,
      "end": 575.4,
      "text": "What makes it important?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 576.54,
      "end": 577.58,
      "text": "She sipped coffee and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 577.66,
      "end": 579.14,
      "text": "brandy before she shook her head."
    },
    {
      "start": 579.84,
      "end": 580.3,
      "text": "I don't know,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 580.72,
      "end": 581.12,
      "text": "she said."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.28,
      "end": 583.04,
      "text": "They'd never tell me.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 583.16,
      "end": 584.14,
      "text": "They promised me"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.2,
      "end": 586.24,
      "text": "500 pounds if I helped them get it."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.88,
      "end": 588.02,
      "text": "Then Floyd said afterward,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 588.18,
      "end": 589.18,
      "text": "after we'd left Joe,"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.68,
      "end": 590.02,
      "text": "that he'd"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.02,
      "end": 590.94,
      "text": "give me 750."
    },
    {
      "start": 592.34,
      "end": 594.35,
      "text": "So it must be worth more than $7,500."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.46,
      "end": 596.06,
      "text": "Oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 596.14,
      "end": 597.1,
      "text": "much more than that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.24,
      "end": 597.68,
      "text": "she said."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.82,
      "end": 598.6,
      "text": "They didn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.72,
      "end": 600.78,
      "text": "pretend that they were sharing equally with me."
    },
    {
      "start": 600.84,
      "end": 602.94,
      "text": "They were simply hiring me to help them."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.98,
      "end": 604.66,
      "text": "To help them how?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 605.94,
      "end": 607.54,
      "text": "She lifted her cup to her lips again.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 607.8,
      "end": 608.48,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.5,
      "end": 610.5,
      "text": "not moving the domineering stare of"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.56,
      "end": 612.32,
      "text": "his yellow-gray eyes from her face,"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.52,
      "end": 613.84,
      "text": "began to make a cigarette."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.88,
      "end": 615.36,
      "text": "Behind them,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 615.38,
      "end": 616.38,
      "text": "the percolator bubbled"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.38,
      "end": 616.94,
      "text": "on the stove."
    },
    {
      "start": 618.24,
      "end": 620.2,
      "text": "To help them get it from the man who had it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 620.46,
      "end": 621.12,
      "text": "she said slowly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.64,
      "end": 622.14,
      "text": "when she had lowered"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.36,
      "end": 622.76,
      "text": "her cup."
    },
    {
      "start": 622.9,
      "end": 625.72,
      "text": "A Russian named Kemidov."
    },
    {
      "start": 625.94,
      "end": 626.04,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.24,
      "end": 627.34,
      "text": "Oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 629.0,
      "end": 629.8,
      "text": "but that's not important,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 630.02,
      "end": 630.86,
      "text": "she objected,"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.28,
      "end": 631.78,
      "text": "and wouldn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.8,
      "end": 632.22,
      "text": "help you."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.74,
      "end": 634.0,
      "text": "She smiled impudently."
    },
    {
      "start": 634.48,
      "end": 636.36,
      "text": "And it's certainly none of your business."
    },
    {
      "start": 637.46,
      "end": 638.42,
      "text": "This was in Constantinople?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 639.2,
      "end": 640.48,
      "text": "She hesitated,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 640.68,
      "end": 641.26,
      "text": "nodded,"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.26,
      "end": 641.64,
      "text": "and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.8,
      "end": 642.72,
      "text": "Marmora."
    },
    {
      "start": 643.33,
      "end": 645.3,
      "text": "He waved his cigarette at her,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 645.36,
      "end": 645.68,
      "text": "saying,"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.26,
      "end": 646.52,
      "text": "go ahead,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 646.68,
      "end": 647.4,
      "text": "what happened then?"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.36,
      "end": 650.12,
      "text": "But that's all I've told you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 650.24,
      "end": 653.0,
      "text": "They promised me 500 pounds to help them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.1,
      "end": 653.8,
      "text": "and I did."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.32,
      "end": 657.38,
      "text": "And then we found that Joe Cairo meant to desert us,"
    },
    {
      "start": 657.42,
      "end": 659.32,
      "text": "taking the falcon with him and"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.4,
      "end": 660.2,
      "text": "leaving us nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.96,
      "end": 662.86,
      "text": "So we did exactly that to him first.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 663.62,
      "end": 665.74,
      "text": "But then I wasn't any better off than I had",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 665.74,
      "end": 666.22,
      "text": "been before,"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.4,
      "end": 669.38,
      "text": "because Floyd hadn't any intention at all of"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.38,
      "end": 672.56,
      "text": "paying me the 750 pounds he had promised me."
    },
    {
      "start": 672.92,
      "end": 675.4,
      "text": "I had learned that by the time we got here."
    },
    {
      "start": 675.76,
      "end": 677.7,
      "text": "He said we would go to New York,"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.74,
      "end": 678.56,
      "text": "where he would sell"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.56,
      "end": 679.72,
      "text": "it and give me my share,"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.95,
      "end": 682.32,
      "text": "but I could see he wasn't telling me the truth."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.168,
      "end": 684.46,
      "text": "Indignation had darkened her",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 684.58,
      "end": 685.16,
      "text": "eyes to violet,"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.8,
      "end": 687.04,
      "text": "and that's why I came to you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 687.18,
      "end": 689.7,
      "text": "to get you to help me learn where the falcon was."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.64,
      "end": 692.08,
      "text": "And suppose you'd got it?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 692.16,
      "end": 692.64,
      "text": "What then?"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.14,
      "end": 696.6,
      "text": "Then I'd have been in a position to talk terms with Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 696.78,
      "end": 697.42,
      "text": "Floyd Thursby."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.464,
      "end": 700.04,
      "text": "Spade squinted at her and suggested,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 700.92,
      "end": 702.96,
      "text": "but you wouldn't have known where to take it to",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 702.96,
      "end": 704.64,
      "text": "get more money than he'd give you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.28,
      "end": 708.02,
      "text": "the larger sum that you knew he expected to sell it for.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 709.18,
      "end": 709.92,
      "text": "I did not know,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 710.08,
      "end": 710.58,
      "text": "she said."
    },
    {
      "start": 711.584,
      "end": 714.12,
      "text": "Spade scowled at the ashes he had dumped on his plate.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 714.78,
      "end": 716.06,
      "text": "What makes it worth all that money,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 716.24,
      "end": 716.74,
      "text": "he demanded."
    },
    {
      "start": 717.02,
      "end": 719.42,
      "text": "You must have some idea at least to be able to"
    },
    {
      "start": 719.48,
      "end": 719.8,
      "text": "guess."
    },
    {
      "start": 720.72,
      "end": 722.0,
      "text": "I haven't the slightest idea.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 722.48,
      "end": 724.38,
      "text": "He directed the scowl at her."
    },
    {
      "start": 725.4,
      "end": 726.02,
      "text": "What's it made of?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 727.296,
      "end": 728.46,
      "text": "Porcelain or black stone,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 728.7,
      "end": 729.28,
      "text": "I don't know."
    }
  ]
}